descript.abstract: Otter Tail County parcel polygons. Updated monthly. When possible GPS coordinate values (sub-centimeter) are used for found section corners. As plat’s, surveys and PLS corners become available new cadastral solutions are created for the Public Land Rectangular Survey System. Metes and Bounds are fitted to the system as a best fit solution. When possible gaps and overlaps are removed at the time of editing.
